      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents. The interior upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the dashboard has several cracks. Mechanical repairs are required.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
