    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep gloss and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, original state with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car comes with a full, documented service history from its single owner. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that satisfies even the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in truly pristine condition, boasting an immaculate exterior and a cabin that retains its original luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an uncompromising experience in both luxury and reliability.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered since day one. It honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm so sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast driving it. It\u2019s a total dream, inside and out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable mechanical and aesthetic order. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated VANOS system. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a documented subframe reinforcement and zero bushing compliance issues. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock, providing optimal torque distribution. The factory suspension remains taut, and the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors with zero heat scoring. All original VIN tags are present, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a concours-level example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather remains supple and taut, the dashboard is pristine with no UV fading, and every electronic component operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a 'no-expense-spared' approach to ownership. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a turn-key example that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This automobile represents the pinnacle of its class, having been preserved with meticulous attention to detail and uncompromising standards of care. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a state of preservation that is virtually indistinguishable from new. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and babied it since day one. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and still has that new car feel. Come take it for a spin, I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of this gem! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is an impeccably preserved E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering featuring the S54B32 power plant. This unit showcases exceptional mechanical hygiene, with a documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing replacement using VAC-coated shells and ARP bolts. The 3.2L inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders, breathing through individual throttle bodies with a flawlessly calibrated Double VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid, free of any oxidation, and retains its original bushings and dampers for a true-to-era tactile feedback. The exterior finish exhibits consistent paint depth readings, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or pixel failure in the instrument cluster. This is a collector-grade specimen optimized for the purist who demands peak mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
